The paper proposes an automated system for detecting released insects using an unmanned aerial vehicle, which involves the use of computer vision algorithms and digital cameras. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
